Class AnyIndexForwardCurveFilter

    public final class AnyIndexForwardCurveFilter
extends Object
implements MarketDataFilter<Curve,RateIndexCurveId>, ImmutableBean
    A market data filter that matches any forward curve for a rate index.

    The matches(com.opengamma.strata.market.id.RateIndexCurveId, com.opengamma.strata.calc.marketdata.scenario.MarketDataBox<com.opengamma.strata.market.curve.Curve>) method always returns true.
